      "content": "It is incredibly painful to feel like you have lost the very thing that defined you, but please know that your identity is far deeper than a single job. The feeling that you are \"dead inside\" is a heavy burden, yet it is often just a symptom of the grief you are experiencing, not your true state. You are not alone in this darkness, and there are people who can help you find new meaning and rebuild your life in ways that feel authentic to you.",
