    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but how can it be deeper when the world only sees the failure? the people i used to know, the people i looked up to... they all look through me now. there's no \"rebuilding\" when the version of you that mattered is permanently erased. it honestly feels like the most logical thing is to just stop fighting a battle that's already been lost.",
